name: BALI MATANGI
description:
The awakening of Bali.

There are huge forces that tries to shut Bali down.

But one by one the pure souls starts to awaken.
The higher consciousness starts to pull it back up again.
The chain will do it collectively in a fractal movement.

No one can put Bali down.
A lot of ancient technologies ,ancient wisdoms and ancient cultures in this place.
The life force will be back to where it belongs,
and sets all to the primal settings.
